OL,3,CMiners strike 40 years on: 12 key
OL,4,Cdates in a dispute that divided Britain
OL,6,FThe 1984-85 holds its place as one of
OL,7,Fthe most acrimonious, bitter and
OL,8,Fcontentious industrial disputes in
OL,9,Fbritish history.
OL,11,FIt cemented political, geographical
OL,12,Fand ideological conflicts that became
OL,13,Fso deeply rooted that their effects in
OL,14,Fmining communities can still be seen
OL,15,Ftoday.
OL,17,FMining families drew on the
OL,18,Fcamaraderie of the pit community amid
OL,19,Fa background of increasing violence as
OL,20,Ftensions rose.
