OL,3,CMiners strike 40 years on: 12 key
OL,4,Cdates in a dispute that divided Britain
OL,6,FNUM President Arthur Scargill says the
OL,7,Fnumerous local strikes constitute a
OL,8,Fnational strike. Not all miners agree,
OL,9,Fwith many in Nottinghamshire refusing
OL,10,Fto walk out.
OL,12,FWakefield miner David Jones becomes
OL,13,Fthe first of eight people to die
OL,14,Fduring the strike. He suffered fatal
OL,15,Fchest injuries after being hit by a
OL,16,Fbrick. Three thousand people attend
OL,17,Fhis funeral a week later in South
OL,18,FKirkby.
