OL,3,CMiners strike 40 years on: 12 key
OL,4,Cdates in a dispute that divided Britain
OL,6,FA special delegate conference in sees
OL,7,Fthe NUM call on all of its members to
OL,8,Fgo on strike.
OL,10,FNUM President Arthur Scargill is
OL,11,Farrested at the Orgreave coking plant,
OL,12,Fnear , and charged with obstruction.
OL,13,FHe is later fined #250.
OL,15,FThe NUM calls for a mass picket
OL,16,Foutside Orgreave, aiming to disrupt
OL,17,Fthe supply of coke to a power station
OL,18,Fin . After several skirmishes between
OL,19,Fstriking miners and police officers in
OL,20,Fthe previous months, the largest
OL,21,Fconfrontation breaks out.
