OL,6,FAs winter starts to bite, 97.3% of
OL,7,FYorkshire miners are on strike.
OL,9,F14 February
OL,11,FThe number of striking miners
OL,12,Fgradually reduces over winter but
OL,13,Fremains at 90%.
